data.description: Spacious 4 bedroom, 2.5 bath ranch featuring over 2000 sq ft  including all four bedrooms. Located in Rothschild with prominent brick exterior, 2-car attached garage with a spacious breezeway and a private back yard with patio area, wooded privacy along the back and a detached storage shed. Inside features updated vinyl plank flooring and fresh grey / white paint selections throughout. Large living area and formal dining room - great for gathering. Functional kitchen with included stainless kitchen appliances. Updated main level bathroom with dual sink vanity and built-in linen storage. Charming rounded archways and built-in cabinetry throughout the home. Owner's suite with connected full bath, recently renovated with a large closet and private shower / toilet area. Large secondary bedrooms (all with ceiling fans) and laminate flooring.,Main level laundry room - included washer & dryer (located off of the back breezeway), just off the kitchen. Additional sq ft in the lower level - open space for future use or offers great storage as is, with a lower level 1/2 bath and 2 small storage rooms. Upgraded electrical service panel (200 amp service). New 240 Volt outlet in the garage added too. Located just a few blocks from Rothschild Elementary School in the D.C. Everest School District. Just a few minutes from Hwy-29 access and Schofield area conveniences. Schedule your showing today!
